column3: “this strain smells phenomenal and the other review is correct it does make you wanna pass out. A really mellow high very relaxing nice way to end the day”

I've smoked over hundreds of strains but this tops it off as the best sativa I tried. Definitel...”"

Definitely. I’ve been reading some of the things that I have been writing while under the spell of the...”

“Excellent strain, nice taste and very uplifting. Highly recommended!”

“True to the Diesel name. Also called Sour Hawaiian" depending on where you pick it up.

column1: This sativa strain has a sweet earthy smell with a hint of diesel fuel scent. The taste is sweet and pungent like most other diesels.
The high onset is quick and energizing. You get a quick jolt of creative energy and the instant need to get up and do something.
Hawaiian Diesel is great for daytime use. The high last about 2...”"

column3: “Really nice sativa, very uplifting. Has a powerful kick. Worth the purchase.”
“Beautiful strain, from the incredibly strong tropical diesel odor, to the great high!”
“You get it all with this strain. You can totally function while  smoking.  Whatever you want to do this will let you and you're smokin' happy!!!”
“Dry Mouth”
“One of the best highs I've ever had. Very happy... wish I had some now. Couldn't help the euphoric feeling the takes over. <3 this strain!!”
